---
title: Nan's Easy Rosemary Lamb Fusilli with Balsamic Apple Salad & Parmesan
description: This simple yet sumptuous dish is absolute decadence from start to finish. From the rich, rosemary-infused lamb mince to the
'al dente' fusilli and delightfully sharp apple salad. It'll be both ready and eaten in record time!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/quick-nans-rosemary-lamb-fusilli-a86b8b7f.jpg
